decision_details:
- Under the the Colombo Port City Economic Commission Act, No. 11 of 2021, it is required to designate the Authorized Persons as Secondary Business of Strategic Importance and to publish the exemptions or incentives proposed for such designated businesses  in the Gazette through an Order and thereafter submit the said Orders in Parliament for information. Accordingly, the proposals made by the Hon. President in his capacity as the Minister of Investment Promotion to submit the Orders under section 53 of the Colombo Port City Economic Commission Act, No. 11 of 2021 published through the following Gazette Notifications to Parliament, were approved by the Cabinet. 

*	the Order published through the Gazette Extraordinary Notification No.2394/06 dated 2024‑07‑22;

*	the Order published through the Gazette Extraordinary Notification No.2394/09 dated 2024‑07‑22;

*	the Order published through the Gazette Extraordinary Notification No.2394/10 dated 2024‑07‑22;

*	the Order published through the Gazette Extraordinary Notification No.2394/11 dated 2024‑07‑22;

